title: MBMBaM 59: Real Talk Live: Face 2 Face 2
description: More real. More talk. More live. We took to the stage at the Cincinnati Shakespeare Company -- which is in Cincinnati, you might have guessed -- to do our second live show ever. Come, share in the yuks! Also, the animosity.
author: shows@mbmbam.com (Justin McElroy)
